<div class="mt-5">
  <p class="h1 text-center">Add your Partner (in crime... or expenses)</p>
  <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3 mt-4">
    <p class="h3 text-center">How does it work?</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Add your partner's email in the form below and send a request</li>
      <li>Your partner will receive an email asking them to sign up for YNAD (You Need A Dashboard)</li>
      <li>Once your partner has signed up, they will be asked to set their preferences as to what you will be able to view from their dashboard.</li>
      <li>You can go to Settings &gt; Permissions to set your preferences of what your partner can view.</li>
      <li>And you're set!</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-4 col-md-2 offset-md-5">
    <%= render 'form' %>
  </div>
</div>
